data.description: Welcome to this inviting, updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home nestled on .87 acres in a peaceful rural setting on Evansville far west side, approx. one mile west of University Pkwy in rural Posey County.  *ASSUMABLE FINANCING AVAILABLE (2.375%)! At just under 2,000 square feet, the home features an oversized living room with a unique vaulted ceiling, exposed beams and an abundance of natural light, and an adjacent home office (which could potentially serve as a fourth bedroom); owner's suite with en-suite, two additional bedrooms, and a full bathroom with stand up shower.   The spacious, fully-applianced kitchen includes lovely white cabinets, newer countertops and attractive tile work.  And off the kitchen is a large laundry/mud room, leading to the attached 2-1/2 car garage.  Perhaps one of the most impressive areas of the home is the expansive 20' x 30' screened-in covered patio overlooking the expansive, serene, tree-line back yard.  And there is even another sizeable deck adjacent to this covered patio, which is home to the large Hot Tub (new in 2022 AND is included)!   Numerous improvements and updates have been completed over the past 4 years and must be seen to appreciate! New roof in 2023 per seller.  This home is truly the essence of quite country living yet is a only short drive to restaurants, retail, grocery, etc. on the west side of Evansville!
